The three-phase steam cleaner (380volt), with professional vacuum cleaner and liquid suction, CLEAN VAPOR PLUS, is a cleaning and sanitizing machine equipped with a steam generator with automatic boiler refilling (5 Lt) and a 1400 Watt two stage vacuum cleaner. It has an external tank for water and detergent supply and one for water refilling. Ideal for cleaning of large industrial and public spaces, professional kitchens, butchers, ovens, cleaning terraces, squares, gyms etc. Steam machine used with satisfaction by cleaning companies.
